parameters: EMW_メッセージウィンドウ指定 1

\EMP Hey hey, are you okay? The thing you're
looking for is in that room over there. Hahaha.
EMW_メッセージウィンドウ強制終了 1
EMW_メッセージウィンドウ指定 2

\EMP Hehe... Your face is quite red. Are you weak
to alcohol, I wonder?
EMW_メッセージウィンドウ強制終了 2
EMW_メッセージウィンドウ指定 3

\EMP My my, you're quite sloppy, Holy Knight-
sama. Shall I lend you a shoulder? Hahaha!
EMW_メッセージウィンドウ強制終了 3

\N<Bray>Well, here is the VIP room you desired. \. So, do
you think there's something you're looking for?

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>────...... Just looking at this alone won't give
me any clues. \. I'm sorry, but may I take a look
around for a bit?

\N<Bray>────... Well, I guess it's fine. But isn't it a
bit one-sided to suddenly appear and start messing
up the room? \. We're letting you into the VIP
room, which is usually off-limits, to save face
for Buster.
\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>─────What do you want me to do?

\CE[79]\N<Bray>Come on, let's have a drink together. Is that
alright?

\CE[79]\CE[78]\CE[84]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(These people, they seem to be up to
something... but... there's no helping it... \. If
it's just a little poison, I can neutralize it
with my magic power...!

\CE[79]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>────\....\....\....\ .Understood.\. But I'm still
working, so just a sip───and please make it a
weaker drink as well.

\CE[79]\N<Bray>You sure have a lot of demands. Well, whatever.
For now, come on, sit here.
\N<Bray>Alright, Rain, let's toast to our encounter!

\N<Bray>Isn't that right? It's a special drink that you
can only have here. Drink more.

\N<Bray>Alright, alright. You want to search this room,
right? Go ahead and do as you please.

\N<Bray>Oh, that's right. Your search item might be in
that room over there. Why don't you take a look?
Hehe...

\N<Bray>Oh, are you already drunk? Walk carefully, it's
dangerous. Hahaha.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Alright... with this, it seems like I can somehow
fight...!

\OC[31]\N<Rain>I managed to escape in the heat of the moment, but
I still don't know the location of the device...
Maybe I have no choice but to capture Buster and
somehow make him talk...

\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>One person is unconscious, but with this situation
and condition, it's 3 against 1... It's tough, but
there's no choice but to do it!
\N<Bray>You! How did you manage to escape?

\N<Elite Thief B>Hey, hey, do you really think you can escape this
far!?
\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(Buster isn't here! This is my chance!)

\CE[78]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I won't run away! Instead, tell me the location of
the device!!

\N<Elite Thief B>Idiot, do you really think you can win in this
situation!?

\N<Bray>I'll throw you back into the training room and
drug you up so much that you'll never be able to
resist again!

\N<Bray>Guh, even weakened, you're still a holy knight!!
You're quite something...!

\N<Bray>But my comrades will be here soon, so it's
pointless resistance!
\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(Ku... Certainly, if it continues like this...)
\n<Caldo>I'm glad, it seems like you're safe!

\CE[94]\OC[30]\N<Phils>Someone named Meryl told me the location here,
chasing after Rain's magical power!

\n<Caldo>Behave yourself, 'Dark Owl'! The entrance is
sealed, so you can't escape!

\OC[31]\N<Rain>A hidden door!? Could this possibly be the path
leading to the location of the device...!?

\n<Caldo>Rain-san, we can't let them escape. We'll handle
this club, so please go after 'Dark Owl'!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Understood. There is likely not only the man from
earlier, but also the leader of 'Dark Owl' -
Buster, in the back. I will definitely capture
them!

\OC[30]\N<Phils>I can sense a strong presence of dark magic ahead,
so please be careful! \. May the blessings of the
Holy Demon be with you...

\n<Caldo>We can't let them escape. We'll handle this club,
so please go after the 'Dark Owl'!
